{"tid":757810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"討論泰國班細路被困就爆4個post，香港人玩滑翔傘失蹤就冇人理","createTime":"2018-07-27T06:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T14:50:43.000Z","uid":66260,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3702feba785747607b355deb623a3de00e8f9043","tid":757810,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:39:34.000Z","msg":"人地國家細路被困，連登仔開成4,5個post又整q&amp;a, 有成幾十人出謀獻策，講下笑又俾人屌，唔知仲以為泰國政府會上連登<br />\n香港自己人失蹤，連登討論post夾埋都唔知有冇30版，當中唔少人仲係幸災樂禍講爛gag風涼話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果連登仔肯用討論幫班泰國細路手既時間精力去諗點救鍾生，唔敢話一定有用，但起碼叫有d建設性，幫助一定大過討論點救其他國家既人<br />\n見到你班人大細超到咁就覺得可恥，香港人條命就算黎到連登都仲係咁賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1810099ec607dccb89b827cb89f3b9e045c1e435","tid":757810,"uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:43:00.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n文字討論就搵得番咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上山搵啦柒頭<br />\n<br />\n你有無去呀？"},{"pid":"4ff41ac904cd632c7eb2618e529ade37f1434016","tid":757810,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:50:08.000Z","msg":"泰國受困山洞少足集中討論post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/732135/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/732135/page/1</a><br />\n泰國受困山洞少足集中討論 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/733321/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/733321/page/1</a><br />\n泰國受困山洞少足集中討論 (3)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/734174/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/734174/page/1</a><br />\n泰國受困山洞少足集中討論 (4)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/734365/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/734365/page/1</a><br />\n泰國受困山洞少足集中討論 (5)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/735163/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/735163/page/2</a><br />\n【泰洞後續】泰國被困少足集中討論 <span style=\"font-size: small;\">(救左出黎仲要後續討論, 連登仔